config BR2_PACKAGE_HELLO_WORLD_SLINT_RUST
    bool "hello_world_slint_rust"
    select BR2_PACKAGE_EUDEV
    select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBINPUT
    select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBXKBCOMMON
    select BR2_PACKAGE_MESA3D
    select BR2_PACKAGE_LIBDRM
    help
      A Rust + Slint GUI demo application for the Luckfox Pico Ultra BW board.

      Uses the Slint backend-linuxkms-noseat with the software renderer.
      Requires:
        - eudev for device enumeration (/dev management)
        - libinput for input device support
        - libxkbcommon for keyboard mapping
        - mesa3d (provides libgbm) for buffer management
        - libdrm for KMS/DRM display output

      The binary will be installed to /usr/bin/hello_world_slint_rust.

